quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  29,46,WE LA TUXHADILU ‘EHLEL-KITABI ‘ILLA BI-ETI HIJE ‘EHSENU ‘ILLAL-LEDHINE DHELEMU MINHUM WE KULU ‘AMENNA BIEL-LEDHI ‘UNZILE ‘ILEJNA WE ‘UNZILE ‘ILEJKUM WE ‘ILEHUNA WE ‘ILEHUKUM WAHIDUN WE NEHNU LEHU MUSLIMUNE
  29,47,WE KEDHELIKE ‘ENZELNA ‘ILEJKEL-KITABE FE-EL-LEDHINE ‘ATEJNAHUMUL-KITABE JU’UMINUNE BIHI WE MIN HA’UULA’ MEN JU’UMINU BIHI WE MA JEXHHEDU BI’AJATINA ‘ILLAL-KAFIRUNE
  29,48,WE MA KUNTE TETLU MIN KABLIHI MIN KITABIN WE LA TEHUTTUHU BIJEMINIKE ‘IDHÆN LARTABEL-MUBTILUNE
  29,49,BEL HUWE ‘AJATUN BEJJINATUN FI SUDURIL-LEDHINE ‘UTUL-’ILME WE MA JEXHHEDU BI’AJATINA ‘ILLA EDH-DHALIMUNE
  29,50,WE KALU LEWLA ‘UNZILE ‘ALEJHI ‘AJATUN MIN RABBIHI KUL ‘INNEMAL-’AJATU ‘INDEL-LAHI WE ‘INNEMA ‘ENA NEDHIRUN MUBINUN
  29,51,‘EWELEM JEKFIHIM ‘ENNA ‘ENZELNA ‘ALEJKEL-KITABE JUTLA ‘ALEJHIM ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LEREHMETEN WE DHIKRA LIKAWMIN JU’UMINUNE
  29,52,KUL KEFA BILLAHI BEJNI WE BEJNEKUM SHEHIDÆN JA’LEMU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU BIL-BATILI WE KEFERU BILLAHI ‘ULA’IKE HUMUL-HASIRUNE
  29,53,WE JESTA’XHILUNEKE BIL-’ADHABI WE LEWLA ‘EXHELUN MUSEMMEN LEXHA’EHUMUL-’ADHABU WE LEJE’TIJENNEHUM BEGTETEN WE HUM LA JESH’URUNE
  29,54,JESTA’XHILUNEKE BIL-’ADHABI WE ‘INNE XHEHENNEME LEMUHITETUN BIL-KAFIRINE
  29,55,JEWME JEGSHAHUMUL-’ADHABU MIN FEWKIHIM WE MIN TEHTI ‘ERXHULIHIM WE JEKULU DHUKU MA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  29,56,JA ‘IBADIJEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘INNE ‘ERDI WASI’ATUN FE’IJAJE FA’BUDUNI
  29,57,KULLU NEFSIN DHA’IKATUL-MEWTI THUMME ‘ILEJNA TURXHA’UNE
  29,58,WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI LENUBEWWI’ENNEHUM MINEL-XHENNETI GUREFÆN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU HALIDINE FIHA NI’ME ‘EXHRUL-’AMILINE
  29,59,EL-LEDHINE SEBERU WE ‘ALA RABBIHIM JETEWEKKELUNE
  29,60,WE KE’EJJIN MIN DABBETIN LA TEHMILU RIZKAHALLAHU JERZUKUHA WE ‘IJAKUM WE HUWE ES-SEMI’UL-’ALIMU
  29,61,WE LE’IN SE’ELTEHUM MEN HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE WE SEHHARE ESH-SHEMSE WEL-KAMERE LEJEKULUNNEL-LAHU FE’ENNA JU’UFEKUNE
  29,62,ELLAHU JEBSUTU ER-RIZKA LIMEN JESHA’U MIN ‘IBADIHI WE JEKDIRU LEHU ‘INNALL-LLAHE BIKULLI SHEJ’IN ‘ALIMUN
  29,63,WE LE’IN SE’ELTEHUM MEN NEZZELE MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN FE’EHJA BIHIL-’ERDE MIN BA’DI MEWTIHA LEJEKULUNNEL-LAHU KULIL-HEMDU LILLAHI BEL ‘EKTHERUHUM LA JA’KILUNE
  29,64,WE MA HEDHIHIL-HEJÆTU ED-DUNJA ‘ILLA LEHWUN WE LA’IBUN WE ‘INNE ED-DAREL-’AHIRETE LEHIJEL-HEJEWANU LEW KANU JA’LEMUNE
  29,65,FE’IDHA REKIBU FIL-FULKI DE’AW ELLAHE MUHLISINE LEHU ED-DINE FELEMMA NEXHXHAHUM ‘ILAL-BERRI ‘IDHA HUM JUSHRIKUNE
  29,66,LIJEKFURU BIMA ‘ATEJNAHUM WE LIJETEMETTA’U FESEWFE JA’LEMUNE
  29,67,‘EWELEM JEREW ‘ENNA XHE’ALNA HEREMÆN ‘AMINÆN WE JUTEHATTEFU EN-NASU MIN HEWLIHIM ‘EFEBIALBATILI JU’UMINUNE WE BINI’METI ELLAHI JEKFURUNE
  29,68,WE MEN ‘EDHLEMU MIMMENI EFTERA ‘ALA ELLAHI KEDHIBÆN ‘EW KEDHDHEBE BIL-HEKKI LEMMA XHA’EHU ‘ELEJSE FI XHEHENNEME METHWEN LILKAFIRINE
  29,69,WEL-LEDHINE XHAHEDU FINA LENEHDIJENNEHUM SUBULENA WE ‘INNALL-LLAHE LEME’AL-MUHSININE